    "In the geographic space, both distances and diversity metrics are easily interpretable because the unit is kilometers on the Earth's surface.",
    "For thematic type and language, the latent dimensions are not directly interpretable.",
    "However, they can be adjusted to make sense by dividing distances by the absolute maximum possible distance in the underlying latent space (multiplied by 2 for internal and circuit diversity).",
    "This scaled distance ranges between 0 and 1.",
